												<p><br />
												Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</p>

												<p>A little while ago, you registered your interest in Step Forward. The programme offers you a chance to secure your future and you&rsquo;re in luck because there&rsquo;s still a chance to apply!</p>

												<p>Summer is fast approaching and you will be thinking about what you want to do when you finish school or college. If you want a year of invaluable paid employment then Step Forward could be right for you. We are looking for are ambitious, committed and adaptable young people ready to get ahead.</p>

												<p>Those who are selected and graduate from Step Forward will have:</p>

												<ul>
													<li>completed 12 months of full time work with a high quality employer</li>
													<li>received a salary of &pound;9,000</li>
													<li>a nationally recognised qualification equivalent to an A-level</li>
													<li>developed essential skills that employers look for such as teamwork, leadership and problem solving</li>
													<li>received support from their own professional mentor to get the most of the year and beyond</li>
													<li>shared their experience with other like-minded people and formed lasting friendshipsâ€‹</li>
												</ul>

												<p>Keep your options open and apply NOW for a great opportunity!</p>

												<p>If we receive your application<strong>&nbsp;before Sunday 31st May</strong>, you will be entered into a&nbsp;<strong>competition to win </strong>one of the following prizes:</p>

												<ul>
													<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&pound;20 Nando&#39;s Voucher</li>
													<li>&nbsp; &pound;20 Topshop voucher</li>
													<li>&nbsp; A personal mentoring session with Jon Yates, co-founder of The Challenge</li>
												</ul>

												<p><strong>Follow the&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://survey.clicktools.com/go?iv=3hel7ksnyaefw&q1=!Account.Id&q2=!Contact.Id&q3=!Step_Forward_Activity__c.Id" target="_blank"><strong>application form</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;steps and apply today.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>

												<p>For hints and tips on how to write an impressive application form and maximise your chances of being selected, check out our&nbsp;<a href="http://www.thestepforwardblog.wordpress.com/">step forward blog</a>.&nbsp;</p>

												<p>Like us on&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthestepforward&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFburLldy1kKrotxUXde202oy5-sA">facebook</a>&nbsp;and follow us on&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThe_StepForward&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNEmI7cjv3v2VjEfxp-Sb6vLykZAAw">twitter</a>&nbsp;to be kept up to date with the latest information.</p>

												<p>Best of luck with your application, and we hope to see you at the Step Forward assessment!</p>

												<p><strong><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please note, if you have already applied and heard back from us then please ignore this email.&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>

												<p>Best wishes,</p>

												<p>Step Forward</p>

